        "name": "Fit for the Role",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Not only are you a flamboyant performer, but you\u2019ve mastered an occult secret that allows you to outfit yourself and your companions with magical visages. You gain the ability to cast *illusory disguise* as a 7th-rank innate occult spell once per day.",
